summary: An ordinance relating to, and providing for, the payment of the cost and expense of the condemnation of a public alley over and across the east 16 feet of Tracts 8, 9, and 10, Claremont Home Tracts, as provided in Ordinance No. 46343 of the City of Seattle, by the issuance and sale of bonds of the district created to pay therefor, and repealing Ordinance No. 48104.
